reviewText: MISS LABELLE IS GREAT!!!  SHE COMES OUT STRONG AND IS SO THROUGHOUT THE SHOW.  HER BACKGROUND SINGERS ARE AMAZING AS WELL AS THE GUEST APPEARANCES BY LUTHER AND MARIAH.  THE AUDIENCE PARTICIPATION IS A PLUS.  SHE IS LOVED BY ALL.ANGIE

reviewText: One of the Great Voices of Soul/R&B music, Patty tears it up! Audio/Visual are all great. Luther Vandross & Maria Carey join Patty on stage & do what they do, SANG! The band & back ground singers where great also. This is a hot concert! I'll say it again, when you get a chance to purchase a concert DVD of a musical icon, you do it!
Title: N/A

reviewText: If you are a Patti LaBelle fan you will love this DVD, as I did. It is a very entertaining concert with variation, a full orchestra, guests to sing duets with, an attractive stage and good editing. The sound and picture quality is excellent!The term 'Diva' gets thrown around too much these days to describe too many. Just because one is popular for five minutes doesn't make her a 'Diva'. Patti LaBelle IS a 'Diva' alongside Aretha, Diana, Tina, Cher and only a few others.

reviewText: She got the Grammy for best Tradional R&B vocal performance in '99 for this concert.She's in top shape.  Her amazing cover of the one "Edith Piaf" song shows you how versatile Patti can be.There's nothing like watching a consumate performer doing her thing.
summary: She got a Grammy for this.  Need I say more!

reviewText: THIS DVD "LIVE ONE NIGHT ONLY/PATTI LABELLE IF YOU ARE A TRUE PATTIE LABELLE FAN AND HAVE ACTUALLY BEEN TO ANY OF HER CONCERTS, OR HAVE HEARD HER SING, THEN YOU KNOW WHAT TO EXPECT, SHE ALWAYS GIVES HER BEST. JUST SEEING AND HEARING LUTHER VANDROSS BROUGHT TEARS TO MY EYES,REMINDING ME OF ANOTHER LOSS OF A TALENTED SINGER. " AGAIN ENJOYED THIS DVD AND HIGHLY RECOMMEND BUYING THIS DVD IF YOU TRULY ENJOY PATTIE. DVD IS CLEAR AUDIO EXCELLENT, MAKES IT SEEM THAT YOU ARE AT THIS CONCERT . IF YOU WANT TO LAUGH, SHOUT ALONG WITH PATTIE MAYBE EVEN CRY WHILE LISTENING TO SOME OF THESE  SONGS, "BUY THIS DVD.  THANK YOU AMAZON.
